title: Vladislav Matviyenko
text: Vladislav Ivanovich Matviyenko (; born 27 September 1967) is a Russian professional <a href="Association%20football">football</a> coach and a former player. As a player, he made his professional debut in the <a href="Soviet%20Second%20League">Soviet Second League</a> in 1989 for <a href="FC%20Okean%20Nakhodka">FC Okean Nakhodka</a>.
